title: Turbo Tax Deluxe 2008
description:
Turbo Tax Deluxe 2008 for windows.

Includes one free state download.

Self extracting installer. 


Will cost you 20 bucks to e-file your state =/ Print for free =]

 <a href="
http://ftpfp.quicken.com/pub/turbotax/2008/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://ftpfp.quicken.com/pub/turbotax/2008/</a>
Pick your states.




Minimum System Requirements

Computer processor                                                
450 MHz 32-bit (x86)
Operating system	Windows 2000 with Service Pack 4
Windows XP (32-bit) Home / Media Center Edition / Pro with Service Pack 2 (or higher)

Windows Vista (32-bit) Home Basic / Home Premium / Business / Ultimate

Note: Administrative rights required



RAM	256 MB
Hard disk space	
Federal: 500 MB for TurboTax (plus up to 500 MB for Microsoft Internet Explorer and Microsoft .NET 2.0 with Service Pack 1)

State: 15 MB

Federal plus State: 500 MB for TurboTax (plus up to 500 MB for Microsoft Internet Explorer and Microsoft .NET 2.0 with Service Pack 1)

CD drive	2X CD-ROM drive
Monitor	
800x600 screen resolution; 1024x768 or higher recommended (Set your screen resolution)

Internet	56 Kbps modem (high-speed connection recommended)
Other software	
Microsoft .NET 2.0 with Service Pack 1 
Microsoft Windows Installer 3 (or higher)
Microsoft Internet Explorer 6 (or higher)
Adobe Flash Player 9 (or higher)
Adobe Reader 8 (or higher)

Note: Installed with TurboTax if not already on your computer
